ight into the middle of the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/0f1475937443cdc29e0166ca7c6c25f0.poster.avif?t=1768791246\" width=1000 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204350/extras/0f1475937443cdc29e0166ca7c6c25f0.webm?t=1768791246\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>And that's not all...</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GLOBAL LEADERBOARDS</strong> to compete with players from all over the world</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LIFE AFTER DEATH</strong> offers active gameplay when you've been caught, but your friends are still alive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>100+ SKINS</strong> for individual character customization</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DETAILED STATISTICS</strong> that track your entire career and every single achievement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DYNAMIC WEATHER</strong> on every map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>IN-GAME WIKI</strong> with a comprehensive tutorial for newcomers</p></li></ul>",
